.TH "nvme_init_get_log_fw_slot" 9 "nvme_init_get_log_fw_slot" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_get_log_fw_slot \- Initialize passthru command for Firmware Slot Information
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_get_log_fw_slot
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "struct nvme_firmware_slot *fw_log "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Passthru command to use
.IP "fw_log" 12
User address to store the log page
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Get Log command with
LID value NVME_LOG_LID_SMART.
